text: Silas Carson (born 8 January 1965) is an English actor, mostly known for portraying several characters in the Star Wars franchise, including Nute Gunray, Ki-Adi-Mundi, Lott Dod and Antidar Williams. He has also been the voice of Ood in Doctor Who. Carson also played roles in many indie films and television shows.
